{
  "video_id": "7LN4L5EMmmc",
  "title": "How the button changed fashion | Small Thing Big Idea, a TED series",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Camille Mart√≠nez Reviewer: Krystian Aparta"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 12183.0,
      "end_time": 14550.0,
      "text": "There are no bad buttons, there are only bad people."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 14575.0,
      "end_time": 15577.0,
      "text": "How does that sound? OK?"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 15602.0,
      "end_time": 16796.0,
      "text": "[Small thing.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 16822.0,
      "end_time": 18600.0,
      "text": "[Big idea.]"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 19356.0,
      "end_time": 21707.0,
      "text": "[Isaac Mizrahi on the Button]"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 23311.0,
      "end_time": 25383.0,
      "text": "No one knows who invented the button."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 25407.0,
      "end_time": 28841.0,
      "text": "It might have shown up as early as 2000 BCE."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 28865.0,
      "end_time": 31148.0,
      "text": "It was decorative when it first started,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 31172.0,
      "end_time": 33396.0,
      "text": "just something pretty sewn onto your clothes."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 33420.0,
      "end_time": 35659.0,
      "text": "Then about 3,000 years later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 35683.0,
      "end_time": 38414.0,
      "text": "someone finally invented the buttonhole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 38438.0,
      "end_time": 40265.0,
      "text": "and buttons were suddenly useful."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 40289.0,
      "end_time": 44400.0,
      "text": "The button and the buttonhole is such a great invention."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 44640.0,
      "end_time": 46230.0,
      "text": "Not only does it slip through the buttonhole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 46254.0,
      "end_time": 48990.0,
      "text": "but then it kind of falls into place,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 48123.0,
      "end_time": 51186.0,
      "text": "and so you're completely secure, like it's never going to open."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 51210.0,
      "end_time": 55350.0,
      "text": "The design of a button hasn't changed much since the Middle Ages."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 55590.0,
      "end_time": 58346.0,
      "text": "It's one of the most enduring designs in history."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 58371.0,
      "end_time": 61592.0,
      "text": "For me, the best buttons are usually round."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 61616.0,
      "end_time": 63995.0,
      "text": "There's either a dome button with a little shank,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 64190.0,
      "end_time": 68553.0,
      "text": "or there's just this sort of round thing with either a rim or not a rim,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68577.0,
      "end_time": 70441.0,
      "text": "either two holes or four holes."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70465.0,
      "end_time": 73174.0,
      "text": "Almost more important than the button is the buttonhole."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73198.0,
      "end_time": 75360.0,
      "text": "And the way you figure that out is:"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75384.0,
      "end_time": 78740.0,
      "text": "the diameter of the button plus the width of the button,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78980.0,
      "end_time": 79428.0,
      "text": "plus a little bit of ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 79452.0,
      "end_time": 82500.0,
      "text": "Before buttons, clothes were bigger --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82524.0,
      "end_time": 84398.0,
      "text": "they were more kind of amorphous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 84422.0,
      "end_time": 86199.0,
      "text": "and people, like, wriggled into them"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86223.0,
      "end_time": 88513.0,
      "text": "or just kind of wrapped themselves in things."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 88537.0,
      "end_time": 92266.0,
      "text": "But then fashion moved closer to the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92290.0,
      "end_time": 94521.0,
      "text": "as we discovered uses for the button."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94545.0,
      "end_time": 100990.0,
      "text": "At one time, it was the one way to make clothes fit against the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 101140.0,
      "end_time": 104689.0,
      "text": "I think the reason buttons have endured for so long, historically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 104713.0,
      "end_time": 107701.0,
      "text": "is because they actually work to keep our clothes shut."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 107725.0,
      "end_time": 108877.0,
      "text": "Zippers break;"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 108901.0,
      "end_time": 111789.0,
      "text": "Velcro makes a lot of noise, and it wears out after a while."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 111814.0,
      "end_time": 114654.0,
      "text": "If a button falls off, you just literally sew that thing on."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 114679.0,
      "end_time": 117171.0,
      "text": "A button is kind of there for the long run."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 117195.0,
      "end_time": 120529.0,
      "text": "It's not just the most elemental design ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120553.0,
      "end_time": 124628.0,
      "text": "it's also such a crazy fashion statement."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 124653.0,
      "end_time": 128180.0,
      "text": "When I was a kid, my mom knit me this beautiful sweater."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 128419.99999999999,
      "end_time": 129192.99999999999,
      "text": "I didn't like it."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 129217.00000000001,
      "end_time": 130759.00000000001,
      "text": "And then I found these buttons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130782.99999999999,
      "end_time": 133578.0,
      "text": "and the minute the buttons were on the sweater, I loved it."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133602.0,
      "end_time": 136536.0,
      "text": "If you don't have good taste and you can't pick out a button,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136560.0,
      "end_time": 138479.0,
      "text": "then let someone else do it, you know?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 138503.0,
      "end_time": 139653.0,
      "text": "I mean that."
    }
  ]
}